

<h1><span class="white">What kind of movie do YOU want to watch?</span></h1>

<div class="whitery center">
    <h2>Instructions:</h2>
    <p>Having trouble picking a movie to watch? Type a genre that you're in the mood for in the search bar.</p>
    <p>You'll receive a random movie suggestion, if you don't like it you can search again. </p>
    <p>If you do want to watch it, click the "add to watch history" button to store the movie in your personal watch history.</p>
    <p>Once a movie is added to your history you can either leave a review on it, or delete it from your watch history.</p>
    <p>Reviewed movies will appear under the "your reviews" tab. Once a movie is deleted from history, its review will also be deleted.</p>
</div>

